                           Other


===============================================================================
===============================================================================


=================================================
         Remove all float and int
=================================================
For now ok.

Others cases are not as a big of an issue because:
- Mostly whole decimal (0.1, 0.2) will encounter rounding error.
- float is enough precision for stats, except maybe 1M+ StatusValues

float -> double
int   -> int64


